    id: 'q-csv-012',
    rawContent: "\\begin{ex}%[0P4V1-3] Cho $\\tan a=2$, tính giá trị của biểu thức $A=\\dfrac{1+\\cos a}{\\sin a}\\left[1-\\dfrac{(1-\\cos a)^2}{\\sin^2a}\\right]$. \\shortans[oly]{1} \\loigiai{ Ta có \\begin{eqnarray*} A&=&\\dfrac{1+\\cos a}{\\sin a}\\left[1-\\dfrac{(1-\\cos a)^2}{\\sin^2a} ight]\\\\\\n &=&\\dfrac{1+\\cos a}{\\sin a}\\left[1-\\dfrac{(1-\\cos a)^2}{1-\\cos^2a} ight]\\\\\\n &=&\\dfrac{1+\\cos a}{\\sin a}\\left[1-\\dfrac{(1-\\cos a)^2}{(1-\\cos a)(1+\\cos a)} ight]\\\\\\n &=&\\dfrac{1+\\cos a}{\\sin a}\\left[1-\\dfrac{1-\\cos a}{1+\\cos a} ight]\\\\\\n &=&\\dfrac{1+\\cos a}{\\sin a}\\left[\\dfrac{1+\\cos a-(1-\\cos a)}{1+\\cos a} ight]\\\\\\n &=&\\dfrac{1+\\cos a}{\\sin a}\\cdot \\dfrac{2\\cos a}{1+\\cos a}\\\\\\n &=&2\\cot a\\\\\\n &=&\\dfrac{2}{\\tan a}\\\\\\n &=&1. \\end{eqnarray*} Vậy $A=1$. } \\end{ex}",
